1
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,800
Security team, listen up.

2
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,360
Stay sharp.

3
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:16,360
Manage your patrol areas well.

4
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,600
No more illegal mining allowed.

5
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:20,840
Do you hear me?

6
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:22,520
Yes, sir.

7
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,780
Especially you three.

8
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,680
Stop causing trouble.

9
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,440
Don't worry, Uncle Tian.

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,400
Uncle Tian, thanks for this.

11
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,240
And thanks to the brothers. Really.

12
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,700
I'll beat you if you cause trouble again. Go.

13
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,770
Thanks to Uncle Tian this time.

14
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,360
Sorry, Uncle Tian.

15
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,920
Sorry.

16
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,080
We really hit the jackpot this time.

17
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:03,580
We're rich.

18
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:17,040
Fan falling off the cliff caused quite a stir.

19
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:21,079
Situ Hongtang added more men to the security team.

20
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:23,520
Mr. Xiao, should I take more men there?

21
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,160
No.

22
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,040
No more accidents at the mine.

23
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,280
We can't alert the police.

24
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,240
In that case,

25
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,920
Find some more people.

26
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,320
New faces this time.

27
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,600
Keep pressuring Situ Hongtang.

28
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,680
She won't let us rest.

29
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,120
We can't make it easy for her either, right?

30
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,410
Don't be afraid to spend money.

31
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,220
We have money. We're rich.

32
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,880
Boss Wu.

33
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,200
Why are you here again?

34
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,280
How many times have I told you?

35
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,880
I can't buy your ore anymore.

36
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,079
We want to have a good talk with Mr. Wu.

37
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:19,209
Don't you understand plain language?

38
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,400
No.

39
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,280
You guys leave first.

40
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,200
Sit.

41
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,280
Gold nugget.

42
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:57,560
Gang, you found a rich mine.

43
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,600
Yeah.

44
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,560
Otherwise, why would we bother Boss Wu?

45
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,680
You...

46
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,280
Name a price.

47
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,160
I really want to.

48
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,200
But I dare not.

49
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,520
What's wrong?

50
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,680
Scared to death of Xiao Tianman?

51
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,320
Who doesn't want to get rich overnight?

52
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:33,440
I'm afraid I won't live to spend it.

53
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,080
We sell the gold,

54
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,880
get some money, and leave.

55
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,680
Who cares about Xiao Tianman then?

56
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,440
Right.

57
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,560
Gang, I'll be honest with you.

58
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:51,040
Reselling gold is illegal.

59
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,960
I really can't take your goods.

60
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,480
Mr. Wu, what about these?

61
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:08,440
Just a gift from the three of us to you.

62
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,800
No, Gang.

63
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
What kind of person do you think I am?

64
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,980
You've always bought our ore, right?

65
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,620
You have connections.

66
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,200
If you don't buy it,

67
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,970
we really have no other way.

68
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,360
So we hope you can show us a way.

69
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:40,240
I do know a few people.

70
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,520
Who?

71
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,920
Gao Shan.

72
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,680
Isn't Gao Shan...

73
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,600
The one who has a beef with Xiao Tianman.

74
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,600
The one who was pushed out, right?

75
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,400
Yeah.

76
00:06:57,840 --> 00:07:00,680
Exactly because he has a beef with Xiao Tianman.

77
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,680
I can't contact him for you.

78
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,820
No need, Mr. Wu.

79
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,680
Just tell us,

80
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,440
how to find this Gao Shan.

81
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,290
It seems to be that place called...

82
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,200
Old Town Underground Boxing Ring.

83
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,440
Thank you, Mr. Wu. Thanks.

84
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,480
Gang, let me remind you.

85
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,240
This Gao Shan...

86
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,680
is not easy to deal with.

87
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:28,480
He's even more vicious than Xiao Tianman.

88
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:34,480
I wish you a fortune, Mr. Wu.

89
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,440
Take care, Gang.

90
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,280
Brother.

91
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,520
You gave it all to him?

92
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,440
Let's go.

93
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,760
Money really talks.

94
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,340
Liao Fei, this is my house.

95
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,440
What do you want?

96
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,960
Sit down.

97
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,020
I'm going to ask you one more time.

98
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,640
How exactly did Xiao Fan die?

99
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,890
I'll tell you one more time.

100
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,380
Xiao Fan's death was an accident.

101
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,140
Qiang from the security team told me,

102
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:05,000
he saw that it was you

103
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:08,810
who pushed Xiao Fan off the cliff with your own hands.

104
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:12,080
Qiang from the security team told you

105
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:15,120
he saw me push Xiao Fan down?

106
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,800
Yes.

107
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,320
Liao Fei.

108
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,760
This must be Xiao Tianman's doing.

109
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,120
You've been fooled by him.

110
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,640
Yang Gang.

111
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,770
Don't pin everything on Xiao Tianman.

112
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,120
Tell me.

113
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,160
How exactly did Xiao Fan die?

114
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,480
I've told you many times.

115
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,280
Xiao Fan's death was an accident. An accident.

116
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,400
Tell me.

117
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,320
How exactly did Xiao Fan die?

118
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,200
I take full responsibility for Xiao Fan's death.

119
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,000
If you have a problem, come at me.

120
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,240
We had no reason to kill Xiao Fan.

121
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,280
You two, sit down.

122
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,920
Sit down.

123
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,640
Liao Fei.

124
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,530
I won't mention you barging into my house.

125
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,720
Let me tell you this.

126
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,360
Regarding Xiao Fan,

127
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:07,560
first of all, it has nothing to do with Qiangzi and Yongzi.

128
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,440
Give me three days.

129
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,090
Once I've handled my business,

130
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,260
I'll give you an explanation.

131
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:20,040
Why should I give you three days?

132
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,730
I just hope you can trust me.

133
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,370
Just three days.

134
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:26,450
If I don't give you an answer in three days,

135
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,200
you can do whatever you want with me.

136
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,890
I'll see you at Xiao Fan's grave in three days.

137
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,210
Xiao Fan's death...

138
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,120
is indeed my responsibility.

139
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,800
Let me handle it.

140
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,660
Xiao Fan's death was an accident.

141
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,240
Look at me.

142
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:13,090
Xiao Fan's death was an accident. Do you understand?

143
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,140
Do you understand?

144
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:25,580
I'll go find Gao Shan this afternoon.

145
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:26,680
In three days,

146
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,480
I will settle everything.
